# 😊 AI Emotion Detector

A Deep Learning based web application that detects human emotions from facial images.

## 🚀 Features
- Upload image and detect emotion
- CNN-based deep learning model
- Colorful UI using Gradio
- Supports multiple emotions

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python
- TensorFlow / Keras
- Gradio
- NumPy

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run the application:
   python app.py

3. Open the link shown in terminal

## ⚠️ Note
- Works best with real human face images
- Emojis/cartoon images may not give accurate results

